<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PDF Fusion - Contract Template</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all' %>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row template-container">
             <div class="card p-4">
                <h5 class="text-center">Internship Agreement</h5>
                <p>This agreement (the "Agreement") is made and entered into on this <i>[signature_date]</i>, by and between <i>[business_name]</i> (the "Company"), located at <i>[company_address]</i>, and <i>[intern_name]</i> (the "Intern"), for the purpose of establishing the terms and conditions of the Internship Program.</p>

                <p><strong>1. Intern Name:</strong> <i>[intern_name]</i></p>
                <p><strong>2. Company:</strong> <i>[business_name]</i></p>
                <p><strong>3. Internship Period:</strong> <i>[intern_duration]</i> months, starting from <i>[start_date]</i> and ending on <i>[end_date]</i>.</p>
                <p><strong>4. Work Hours:</strong> The intern agrees to work <i>20 hours per week</i>, with the schedule to be agreed upon by both parties. Work hours may be adjusted as necessary.</p>
                <p><strong>5. Stipend:</strong> The intern will receive a stipend of $<i>[stipend_amount]</i> per month, payable on a monthly basis. The stipend is subject to applicable taxes and deductions as required by law.</p>

                <p><strong>6. Responsibilities:</strong> During the internship, the intern will gain hands-on experience in the field of <i>[intern_department]</i>. The intern is expected to assist in various tasks such as:
                <ul>
                    <li>Participating in team meetings and discussions.</li>
                    <li>Assisting with research and data collection.</li>
                    <li>Contributing to ongoing projects under the supervision of the assigned mentor.</li>
                    <li>Attending training and development sessions as required.</li>
                    <li>Completing all tasks assigned within the deadlines set by the supervisor.</li>
                </ul></p>

                <p><strong>7. Confidentiality:</strong> The intern agrees to maintain confidentiality regarding all proprietary and confidential information that may be shared during the course of the internship. This obligation will continue even after the internship ends.</p>

                <p><strong>8. Non-Compete Clause:</strong> The intern agrees not to engage in any activities that directly compete with the business interests of the Company during the internship and for a period of one year after the internship ends, within the geographical area where the Company operates.</p>

                <p><strong>9. Termination:</strong> Either party may terminate this Agreement at any time with or without cause by providing <i>two weeks' notice</i> in writing. In the event of early termination, the intern will be compensated for work performed up to the termination date.</p>

                <p><strong>10. Final Report:</strong> Upon completion of the internship, the intern will submit a final report detailing the tasks completed, skills learned, and overall experience gained during the internship period. This report will be reviewed by the supervisor and discussed during the final evaluation.</p>

                <p class="text-muted">This Agreement does not constitute an employment relationship, and the intern shall not be entitled to any employee benefits, including but not limited to healthcare, paid time off, or retirement benefits.</p>

                <p><strong>11. Acknowledgment:</strong> By signing this Agreement, both the Company and the Intern acknowledge that they have read, understood, and agree to the terms outlined above.</p>

                <p>Signed by: __________________ (Supervisor) &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Date: <i>[signature_date]</i></p>
                <p>Signed by: __________________ (Intern) &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Date: <i>[intern_sign_date]</i></p>

                <p><strong>12. Additional Terms:</strong> Any additional terms or conditions not covered in this Agreement will be addressed and agreed upon by both parties in writing.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
